room_title: Escape room "The Time Machine: Deja Vu" by Dynamic Escape Rooms in Phoenix
room_address: 1797 W University Dr, Suite 168, Tempe AZ 85281
room_description: During your extended vacation on present-day Earth, you've been posing as a medicine man to get away from the chaos of the universe, but your vacation is about to suddenly come to an end. An unexpected message arrives from somewhere in time requesting your urgent assistance. A close friend is in grave danger and time is running out. Can you decipher the message before it's too late?
